eligibility.inclusivecriteria:
Residents in the elderly home will be eligible according to the following inclusion criteria: 
(1). Age greater than or equal to 65 years;
(2). With suboptimal blood pressure control (SBP greater than 120 or DBP greater than 80 mmHg)
(3). Taking medications for chronic disease management;
(4). Currently attending medical clinics for refill of medications.
